    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <h3>Özel İstanbul Bölge Hastanesi</h3>
    <p> Founded nearly 250 years ago with the fundamental belief that every person deserves access to the very best care,  Özel İstanbul Bölge Hastanesi is one of the nation’s most comprehensive, integrated academic healthcare systems, from dependable primary care to the most sophisticated specialties.

In collaboration with two world renowned academic institutions, Sacit Cinsoy Medicine and Sancaktepe University, Özel İstanbul Bölge Hastanesi is a leader in medical education, groundbreaking research, and innovative clinical care. This single-minded focus on excellence provides our premier healthcare professionals access to cutting-edge technology, leading telehealth resources and clinical trials.

Recognized nationally for quality and excellence, Özel İstanbul Bölge Hastanesi is ranked as the 4th hospital in the nation by Turkey News & World Report. İstanbul’s top-ranked hospital for 20 years, with more “Top Doctors” than any other hospital in the country, Özel İstanbul Bölge Hastanesi is a destination for advanced, innovative medical and surgical care. </p>
